data.name: LAP SPONGES
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% Cotton fabric

## STERILIZATION
- Non Sterile, Ethylene oxide and Steam Sterilization

## PRESENTATIONS
- Sterile and non-sterile
- With X-Ray Band and Blue Loop (holder)
- Open and Folded Edges
- White and Green Color

## PERFORMANCE
- Highly Absorbent
- Sewn Without open Edges

## AVAILABLE SPECIFICATIONS
- Cotton Yarn: 40’s / 36’s / 32’s / 21’s
- Mesh: 13th / 17th
- Color: White / Green / Blue
- Size: 20x20cm / 20x30cm / 30x30cm/ 40x40cm / 45x45cm / 50x60cm /90x8cm
- Layer: 4p / 6p / 12p
- Loop: With or without cotton loop (blue loop)
- Type: Pre-washed / non-washed/sterile / non-sterile
